    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A wave of cold energy spreads out from you. Each creature in a 15-foot cone must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 2d6 cold damage and gains a level of slowed until the end of its next turn. On a success, it takes half as much damage, and suffers no additional effect.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Overcharge Tech.</strong></em> When you cast this power using a tech slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 1st. At 3rd level or above, the speed reduction increases to 20 feet. At 5th level or above, the speed reduction increases to 30 feet.</p>\n",
